# ============= PROJECT-SPECIFIC PATTERNS =============

# Legacy web projects - ignore problematic paths
**/legacy/**                  # Legacy codebases
**/deprecated/**              # Deprecated modules
**/vendor/**                  # Third-party dependencies
**/cache/**                   # Cache directories
**/logs/**                    # Log files
**/*.min.js                   # Minified files
**/*.min.css                  # Minified stylesheets

# FastAPI/Django projects - modern Python stack
**/migrations/**              # Database migrations
**/staticfiles/**             # Collected static files
**/media/**                   # User uploaded files
**/__pycache__/**             # Python cache
**/celery-beat-schedule       # Celery scheduler

# Analytics and data science projects
**/raw-data/**                # Raw datasets
**/processed-data/**          # Processed datasets
**/*.csv                      # Large CSV files
**/*.parquet                  # Parquet data files
**/models/**/*.pkl            # Saved ML models
**/notebooks/.ipynb_checkpoints/  # Jupyter checkpoints

# Cloud and infrastructure
**/terraform/.terraform/      # Terraform state
**/.env.local                 # Local environment vars
**/.env.production            # Production secrets
**/docker-data/**            # Docker volume data

# insides
**/real-time-analytics-pipeline-INSIGHTS/app/models/


